<item>
            <title>[LU-10838] replay-single/89 fails with a single client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10838</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when a single client is used, lfs df in client_up() doesn&apos;t really wait for recovery completion: ost1 is still waiting for missing client (just remoounted) and doesn&apos;t let new client to connection leaving corresponding OSC connection inactive. then check for ltd_active in lov_iocontrol() skips that inactive connection and lfs df finishes. in presence of another client similar ltd_active is set, so lfs df blocks on OSC connection to restarted ost1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>single client setup</environment>
